{"tid":762330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"A片女導分享「陰道粉彩錠」　少女心噴發體液亮晶晶","createTime":"2018-07-31T07:32:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T12:18:05.000Z","uid":180192,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8518e439356e7ea0fff86fa6064bdf1f5a3043","tid":762330,"uid":180192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T07:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/153130_4ce952f92fadda8894a86c3fbed54984.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F153130_4ce952f92fadda8894a86c3fbed54984.jpg&h=f4fd1821&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日朋友送她一組陰道粉彩錠，喜不勝收的駒場雪利酒馬上又PO文分享。翻攝推特<br />\n<br />\n創意無極限！日本知名女性A片導演「駒場達令」近日在《推特》上分享了一種奇特的新產品，號稱只要把照片中的膠囊放入下體，少女心噴發後的體液竟會閃閃發光，強烈推薦給所有喜歡自拍不雅照PO網的女性，文章露出後引發熱烈討論，一度還衝上推特熱門文章，「天啊！我好想用用看喔，哪裡買的到啊！」<br />\n<br />\n身為曾發行「魔鏡號」等膾炙人口大作知名片商DEEPS的專屬導演，駒場達令經常在《推特》上分享一些拍片經驗與片場八卦，加上其女性身份吸引不少熱愛AV文化的粉絲，近日朋友送她一組陰道粉彩錠，喜不勝收的駒場達令馬上又PO文分享，「會流出很適合PO在SNS上面的體液喔！」不過也有網友擔心事後很難清理，「請問這是下次拍片的主題嗎！」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/153135_656d1c023523f37441bd199420786618.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F153135_656d1c023523f37441bd199420786618.jpg&h=5e977d6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n身為曾發行「魔鏡號」等膾炙人口大作知名片商DEEPS的專屬導演，駒場達令經常在《推特》上分享一些拍片經驗與片場八卦。翻攝推特<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/153138_d2aa59d3fb4506a12fe9be79c340fe2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F153138_d2aa59d3fb4506a12fe9be79c340fe2a.jpg&h=f9786cf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文章露出後引發熱烈討論，一度還衝上推特熱門文章。翻攝推特<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180731/1401473/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180731%2F1401473%2F&d=y8GnNjpPWm%2BETVwSsq17p9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=8067f484\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180731%2F1401473%2F&h=d5c49e26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180731/1401473/</a>"},{"pid":"233e58cf8f1aeeacd91f1b8cd8e1546d586fe873","tid":762330,"uid":17231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T07:35:21.000Z","msg":"有無使用後效果相睇呀？"},{"pid":"3a08924fa61d8b525f4b69c3c9ccbd235074549e","tid":762330,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T07:35:49.000Z","msg":"如果你係熄燈扑嘢又點會睇到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4552537b3f1b05c58d81973a0b5a0241a79e8f3","tid":762330,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T07:43:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e0e554bfffa1e40946a4302b3c8c44d3e8bdee2","tid":762330,"uid":66822,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T07:44:19.000Z","msg":"d中文咁難明嘅"},{"pid":"bc865981bf7b63d1921392b91eed9b12cf00c749","tid":762330,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T07:49:53.000Z","msg":"咁都叫新聞<br />\n記者真好做"},{"pid":"fc042a169c23003644f1902025a0a699aa84b495","tid":762330,"uid":123296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T07:56:18.000Z","msg":"最重要嘅圖都無<br />\n廢文"},{"pid":"718e69069fd1d5745785aa181e45abacd4e827cd","tid":762330,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:02:01.000Z","msg":"純文字討論？"},{"pid":"6ae4d0e52eb0a6ff1197a9e99bd6097d30dd9a46","tid":762330,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:14:51.000Z","msg":"幾時有拍拍下中出埋導演系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c319121d89f15747a1277e4f6d3afed039a7a9","tid":762330,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a08924fa61d8b525f4b69c3c9ccbd235074549e","tid":762330,"uid":38904,"like"